name: Neslihan Atagül
description:
A request of @Despotism. (Great taste, man. She's absolutely gorgeous.)

Neslihan Atagül is a Turkish actress and social media celebrity with around 14M followers on Instagram.

1000-step TI trained on a dataset of 20 images with my usual settings.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
